<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢٧ (١)</span> - ٣٨٤ هـ) <span class="c2">(٩٣٩ - ٩٩٤ م)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>المحسن بن علي بن محمد بن داود بن ابراهيم<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
